      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, did you just say \"step on a goblin's tail\"? I'm not really looking for metaphors or anything like that, I just need to know if there are specific things in this paragraph that would make me personally liable for huge amounts of money. Are there any \"hidden\" risks in this wording that I should be worried about?",
